    "consequences" : [
    
    
    
    "After replacing the body or sheetmetal parts in the area of the vehicle identification number, the original vehicle identification number must be re-imprinted on the new body or new sheetmetal part."
    ,
    
    {
    
    
    "type" :
    
    
    "static"
    ,
    
    "inputs" : {
    
    
    "html" :
    
    
    "                     An incorrectly imprinted vehicle identification number must be permanently crossed through with an                      <b>X</b>                      so that it remains legible. In such cases, the applicable vehicle identification number must be imprinted above the crossed out number in the replacement field.                 "
    
    }
    
    }
    ,
    
    
    "For information on procedures for documenting a newly imprinted vehicle identification number in the vehicle documents or in the case of questions concerning homologation, contact the importer of the respective country."
    ,
    
    
